WEBVTT

00:01.521 --> 00:05.023
===MUTANT X Once Around / s02.ep16===

00:09.509 --> 00:11.111
WHAT'S WRONG?

00:11.111 --> 00:12.714
BEING THIS CLOSE TO A COURTHOUSE
GIVING YOU BAD MEMORIES?

00:12.714 --> 00:14.317
NO.

00:14.317 --> 00:15.919
I HAVE BETTER THINGS TO DO WITH
MY TIME THAN SIT AROUND WAIT

00:15.919 --> 00:18.723
FOR SOME LOW-RENT HOOD.

00:19.123 --> 00:21.126
YEAH, A HOOD THAT HAPPENS
TO BE A KEY WITNESS IN PUTTING

00:21.126 --> 00:23.931
AWAY THE LEADER OF A MAJOR
CRIME SYNDICATE IN THE COUNTRY.

00:23.931 --> 00:25.133
EXACTLY.

00:25.534 --> 00:27.937
YOU KNOW, ADAM'S GOT US PULLING
BABYSITTING DUTY FOR SOME

00:27.937 --> 00:30.341
PUREBRED GRADE A RAT.

00:33.145 --> 00:35.549
HEY, UH, ONE
OF YOU GUYS WANT TO...

00:35.549 --> 00:37.552
WANT TO CRACK
THE WINDOW OR SOMETHING?

00:37.552 --> 00:40.357
I'M BURNING UP BACK HERE, UH?

00:41.958 --> 00:43.561
BETTER, PRINCESS?

00:43.962 --> 00:46.366
NO. NO, LOOK,
I DO NOT WORK WITH A/C.

00:46.366 --> 00:48.369
OKAY? IT DRIES UP MY SINUSES.

00:48.769 --> 00:51.172
WILL... WILL YOU
JUST CRACK A WINDOW?

00:56.381 --> 00:58.784
I THINK YOU'LL BE A LOT
HAPPIER ONCE VIC TESTIFIES.

00:58.784 --> 01:00.787
WITHOUT HIM, RAYMOND WALKS.

01:00.787 --> 01:04.794
THIRD TIME IN NEARLY A DECADE.

01:07.197 --> 01:10.403
HEY, SILVERMAN, GOOD LUCK TODAY.

01:10.403 --> 01:13.607
WHAT? ARE YOU
AFRAID TO SHAKE MY HAND?

01:14.007 --> 01:16.412
I'M NOT AFRAID OF YOU.

